long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Fleeing the Complex is a captivating and humorous point-and-click adventure game where players strategize to escape from a high-security prison. Set in a remote, snowy fortress, the game presents a variety of unique challenges and choices that influence the storyline, leading to multiple endings. 

Players must use their wit to solve puzzles and interact with a cast of quirky characters, each adding depth and humor to the escape saga. With its clever animations and unexpected twists, Fleeing the Complex offers a fresh and engaging experience that tests problem-solving skills and keeps players guessing at every turn.

If you have any questions about our Fleeing the Complex game extension or just want to give us some feedback, feel free to send us a message or write a review! We'd love to hear from you. You can mouse over to Support tab on the extension, then click on "visit the developer's support site" to contact us.

If you wish to remove this extension, follow this steps:
1. Click the 3-dot icon at the top-right corner of your screen.
2. Hover your mouse on More tools then click Extensions.
3. Find the Fleeing the Complex game extension.
4. Press "Remove"
